  <div class="container--narrow container">

    <h2 class="s5-process__heading">What To Expect During Your Rejuvenating Vitamin C Facial Experience</h2>

    <div class="s5-process__body">
      <p class="s5-process__intro">From the moment you arrive at Menon Medispa, our team is dedicated to ensuring you have a relaxing, results-driven experience. Here is a step-by-step guide to your Vitamin C Facial treatment so you know exactly what to expect.</p>

      <h3 class="s5-process__step-heading">Consultation &amp; Skin Assessment (5-10 minutes)</h3>
      <p class="s5-process__text">Your treatment begins with a thorough skin consultation with one of our licensed estheticians. We will assess your skin type, discuss your skincare concerns and goals, and customize the treatment to address your specific needs. This ensures you receive the most effective Vitamin C Facial for your unique skin.</p>

      <h3 class="s5-process__step-heading">Deep Cleansing &amp; Preparation (10-15 minutes)</h3>
      <p class="s5-process__text">We begin by thoroughly cleansing your skin to remove makeup, oils, and impurities. This essential preparation step ensures that your skin is ready to receive the full benefits of the Vitamin C treatment and allows our professional formulations to penetrate deeply and effectively.</p>

      <h3 class="s5-process__step-heading">Professional C Microdermabrasion &amp; Treatment (25-30 minutes)</h3>
      <p class="s5-process__text">The centerpiece of your experience, our professional microdermabrasion gently exfoliates and resurfacing your skin while our potent Vitamin C complex is massaged in using specialized techniques. This combination maximizes absorption and stimulates circulation, delivering antioxidants deep into the skin layers for optimal brightening and anti-aging results.</p>

      <h3 class="s5-process__step-heading">Hydration &amp; Protection (10-15 minutes)</h3>
      <p class="s5-process__text">We complete your treatment with a customized hydrating mask and protective serum to lock in all the benefits of your Vitamin C Facial. Your skin will be left feeling deeply moisturized, refreshed, and visibly radiant. We will also provide you with personalized aftercare recommendations to extend and enhance your results at home.</p>

      <h3 class="s5-process__step-heading">Completely Comfortable &amp; Safe</h3>
      <p class="s5-process__text">Our Vitamin C Facial is designed to be a relaxing, enjoyable experience with no pain or discomfort. The treatment is non-invasive with no needles and no downtime, making it the perfect lunchtime treatment. Most clients experience only a mild, pleasant warming sensation during the treatment and leave with an immediate, visible improvement in their skin's brightness and texture.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

